commit.message:
tree.c (debug_binfo): Make printf format match arguments.

1998-06-10  John Carr  <jfc@mit.edu>
	* tree.c (debug_binfo): Make printf format match arguments.
	* error.c (OB_PUTI): Make printf format match arguments.

From-SVN: r20401

+1998-06-10  John Carr  <jfc@mit.edu>
